---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Services - Kate Career Coach"
    description="Coaching services to help you navigate your career journey with confidence"
>
    <div class="py-12 sm:py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-4">
                    What I Offer
                </p>
                <h1
                    class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground mb-6"
                >
                    1-to-1 coaching
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8"
                >
                    Private coaching tailored to where you are and where you want to go.
                    Pick the format that fits your situation.
                </p>
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground mb-3">Who I work with</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <span class="font-sans text-sm font-medium bg-secondary/50 text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Do-ers moving into strategy</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-sm font-medium bg-secondary/50 text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Freelancers building their own thing</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-sm font-medium bg-secondary/50 text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Leaders at a plateau</span>
                    <span class="font-sans text-sm font-medium bg-secondary/50 text-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-full">Designers stepping into leadership</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-stretch">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div class="relative bg-primary p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col">
                    <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 sm:left-8">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most popular</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="absolute top-5 sm:top-6 right-5 sm:right-6 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider">3 months</p>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary-foreground mb-4 mt-2">
                        The Pivot Program
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-primary-foreground/70 mb-4 flex-grow">
                        We go deep, build momentum, and don't let you off the hook.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
                        <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Good fit if:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You're ready to make a real move, not just think about it
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You want accountability over time, not a one-off chat
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You're navigating a significant career pivot
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <details class="mb-4 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary-foreground/60 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary-foreground/90 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            What you actually get
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary/60 flex-shrink-0"></span>6 × 70-minute sessions
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary/60 flex-shrink-0"></span>Email support between sessions
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary/60 flex-shrink-0"></span>Personalized action plans
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-6">
                        <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary-foreground">€610</p>
                        <span class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/50 line-through">€720</span>
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider">Save €110</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-white w-full">Explore fit</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="relative bg-card p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col group">
                    <p class="absolute top-5 sm:top-6 right-5 sm:right-6 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">4 weeks</p>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-4">
                        The Clarity Program
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-muted-foreground mb-4 flex-grow">
                        Cut through the noise, find what's actually blocking you, and leave with a plan.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-secondary/40 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
                        <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Good fit if:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You're stuck and can't figure out why
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You need clarity fast, without a long commitment
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>Staying undecided is costing you more than deciding
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <details class="mb-4 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            What you actually get
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>4 × 70-minute sessions
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>Email support between sessions
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>Values & strengths assessment
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                    <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-6">
                        <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground">€430</p>
                        <span class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground line-through">€480</span>
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Save €50</span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-primary w-full">Explore fit</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="relative bg-card p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col group">
                    <p class="absolute top-5 sm:top-6 right-5 sm:right-6 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">70 mins</p>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-4">
                        No Strings Attached
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-muted-foreground mb-3 flex-grow">
                        No ongoing commitment. Just get it done.
                    </p>
                    <div class="bg-secondary/40 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4">
                        <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Good fit if:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You have a specific challenge to solve right now
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You don't need ongoing coaching — just a sharp session
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-foreground flex items-start gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1.5"></span>You want an outside perspective on something concrete
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <details class="mb-4 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            What you actually get
                        </summary>
                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>1 × 70-minute session
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>Comprehensive written follow-up
                            </li>
                            <li class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/40 flex-shrink-0"></span>One clear next step
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-6">€120</p>
                    <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-primary w-full">Explore fit</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground text-center mt-8 sm:mt-10 max-w-xl mx-auto px-2">
                If the investment feels out of reach right now, reach out anyway. I occasionally offer reduced rates for people in career transitions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Client quote -->
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-secondary">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
                <blockquote class="font-serif text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl text-foreground leading-snug mb-6">
                    "Kate's greatest talent is to uncover your belief system — and she does it at an incredible speed. That's what makes each session so effective."
                </blockquote>
                <p class="font-serif text-base text-foreground/60">Pauline</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Corporate Training Section -->
    <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 sm:gap-16 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary mb-4">
                            For organisations
                        </p>
                        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6">
                            Corporate Training
                        </h2>
                        <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-primary-foreground/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Career development isn't just a personal challenge — it's an organisational one too. I work with companies to build career clarity, retention, and confidence across teams through workshops, group sessions, and tailored programmes.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/intro-call" class="btn-white">Get in touch</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6">
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-primary-foreground mb-2">Career Development Workshops</h3>
                            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/70">Half-day or full-day group sessions on career clarity, transitions, and navigating uncertainty at work.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6">
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-primary-foreground mb-2">Team Coaching Programmes</h3>
                            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/70">Structured multi-week programmes for teams going through change, growth, or strategic pivots.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-primary-foreground/10 border border-primary-foreground/20 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6">
                            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-primary-foreground mb-2">Tailored to Your Needs</h3>
                            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/70">Every organisation is different. Let's talk about what your team actually needs and build from there.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
